# Historical swf-remote alarms cron.
#
# The live alarm runner moved to swf-monitor on pandaserver02. Keep the old
# swf-remote cron disabled. This file is retained only as rollback/reference.

# Old cadence, intentionally commented:
# */5 * * * * /home/admin/github/swf-remote/alarms/.venv/bin/swf-alarms-run --config /home/admin/github/swf-remote/alarms/config.toml >> /var/log/swf-alarms/cron.log 2>&1
